//   HTTP 2xx                  → nextStep(__rtNextStepSuccess)  
//   Unknown host              → nextStep(__rtNextStepFailure)  
//   Timeout                   → nextStep(__rtNextStepFailure)  
//   Connection failure        → nextStep(__rtNextStepFailure)  
